522
00:39:04,217 --> 00:39:07,084
so we can keep getting rich teaching them.

523
00:39:07,178 --> 00:39:10,670
It's a game. One you just played very, very well.

524
00:39:10,765 --> 00:39:12,676
Where's your beer?

