00:39:12,767 --> 00:39:15,099
I decided to wait for the rum.
I hear it's good down here.

526
00:39:15,186 --> 00:39:17,768
Everything's good down here.
You deserve a taste of all of it.

527
00:39:34,956 --> 00:39:37,197
I think that since we're here on this island,

528
00:39:37,292 --> 00:39:41,205
there's things we can do on
