529
00:39:41,921 --> 00:39:43,957
Come on, you deserve it.

530
00:39:48,469 --> 00:39:52,212
Look, I don't mean to hurt your
feelings, but this isn't gonna happen.

531
00:39:52,307 --> 00:39:54,468
Would you tell my friend I went back to the condo?

532
00:39:54,601 --> 00:39:57,217
You don't know what you're missing.

533
00:39:58,897 --> 00:40:00,478
Thanks anyway.

