00:40:25,924 --> 00:40:27,460
- Leave me alone!
- Listen to me.

535
00:40:53,034 --> 00:40:54,114
Are you all right?

536
00:40:54,202 --> 00:40:57,319
It's okay. Just wait a minute.

537
00:40:59,749 --> 00:41:01,034
Wait a minute.

538
00:41:01,834 --> 00:41:03,995
Can I look at this?

539
00:41:04,087 --> 00:41:05,952
