sprained a lot of ankles.

542
00:41:13,888 --> 00:41:15,503
Mostly mine.

543
00:41:21,604 --> 00:41:25,062
You should ice this.

544
00:41:25,733 --> 00:41:27,519
You should also report that guy.

545
00:41:34,575 --> 00:41:36,691
