00:48:03,964 --> 00:48:06,876
and we both ended up surrounded by crooks?

590
00:48:09,804 --> 00:48:13,046
Sonny Capps is thrilled. McDeere was dazzling.

591
00:48:13,140 --> 00:48:15,722
I think we ought to pull Lamar out
of that tax seminar in Washington

592
00:48:15,810 --> 00:48:17,471
and send Mitch instead.

593
00:48:17,561 --> 00:48:20,348
Let him take the jet. Any problem with that, Bill?

594
00:48:20,439 --> 00:48:22,896
No. No, no problem.

595
00:48:22,983 --> 00:48:25,224
So far the kid's been real predictable.

596
00:48:26,529 --> 00:48:30,772
If you're even half right, you're gonna
need some help. What does Abby think?

597
00:48:32,034 --> 00:48:33,820
I haven't told her.

598
00:48:37,039 --> 00:48:38,620
I guess...

599
00:48:40,334 --> 00:48:42,950
I guess I don't want it to be real.

