718
00:56:25,007 --> 00:56:27,794
Okay! Okay.

719
00:56:31,680 --> 00:56:33,466
Just let me think.

720
00:56:34,892 --> 00:56:38,885
His name was Julio Iglesias.

721
00:56:42,357 --> 00:56:44,018
No! No!

722
00:56:46,904 --> 00:56:48,144
Great!

723
00:56:48,906 --> 00:56:50,817
Just great.

724
00:56:50,908 --> 00:56:53,775
You want to ask him a few questions now?

725
00:57:24,816 --> 00:57:27,353
I think this is a carefully balanced proposal.

726
00:57:27,444 --> 00:57:30,732
I think it's high-minded and I think it's fair-minded.

727
00:57:30,822 --> 00:57:34,280
In other words, it's got
something in it to offend everyone.

