00:58:24,668 --> 00:58:26,033
Hey, brother.

742
00:58:29,172 --> 00:58:32,664
Brother, go down the steps towards the pool.

743
00:58:32,759 --> 00:58:34,841
Here you go, brother.

744
00:58:36,096 --> 00:58:38,428
- Voices from the Wall.
- Thanks a lot.

745
00:58:38,515 --> 00:58:39,630
Oh, yeah.

746
00:58:39,725 --> 00:58:40,840
Mister.

747
00:58:53,196 --> 00:58:54,811
Who killed Eddie Lomax?

748
00:58:54,906 --> 00:58:58,023
Go over and sit next to the man on the bench.

749
00:59:16,470 --> 00:59:19,086
I appreciate your coming, Mr. McDeere.

750
00:59:19,181 --> 00:59:21,547
I'll call you Mitch, if I may?

751
00:59:22,517 --> 00:59:25,179
My name is Voyles. Denton Voyles.

752
00:59:25,270 --> 00:59:26,851
I'm with the Department of Justice.

753
00:59:26,938 --> 00:59:29,224
What happened to Eddie Lomax?

754
00:59:29,941 --> 00:59:34,105
We've been investigating Bendini,
