That's what Kozinski and Hodges were trying to do.

791
01:01:47,996 --> 01:01:50,112
You have to think this over.

792
01:01:50,207 --> 01:01:54,416
Meanwhile, you and your wife have to
behave as though everything is normal.

793
01:01:56,630 --> 01:01:58,962
Now don't discuss this with anyone,

794
01:02:00,467 --> 01:02:02,549
but make a decision.

795
01:02:02,636 --> 01:02:06,254
If you help us, we'll make it worth your while.

796
01:02:06,348 --> 01:02:07,963
