821
01:03:41,318 --> 01:03:43,900
They can get to anyone, anywhere.

822
01:03:44,904 --> 01:03:46,394
What can you do?

823
01:03:46,489 --> 01:03:49,856
Your brother comes up for parole soon, doesn't he?

824
01:03:50,577 --> 01:03:54,695
You cooperate with us, I'll
guarantee the board will be grateful.

825
