Well, I mean, as far as I can remember.

847
01:05:47,861 --> 01:05:50,273
It wasn't exactly a sequential conversation.

848
01:05:50,363 --> 01:05:52,445
There was a lot of yelling, mostly by me.

849
01:05:52,532 --> 01:05:57,117
Mitch, we're always doing battle with the government.

850
01:05:57,203 --> 01:06:01,037
If it isn't the Justice Department,
it's the IRS, and you know what?

851
01:06:01,166 --> 01:06:03,452
