but it costs you everything.

856
01:06:18,349 --> 01:06:20,715
Now, I don't want you to worry about this.

857
01:06:20,810 --> 01:06:24,302
It's gotten serious enough.
We'll have to get into it legally.

858
01:06:24,397 --> 01:06:28,561
I guess the only other question
is, who do we bill this hour to?

859
01:06:31,404 --> 01:06:33,736
How about the FBI?

860
01:07:06,773 --> 01:07:10,265
I can't believe that. That is so weird.

861
