I was just thinking about you.

862
01:07:14,405 --> 01:07:17,272
Somebody's burning leaves outside, did you smell it?

863
01:07:17,408 --> 01:07:19,694
It reminded me of the time...

864
01:07:25,083 --> 01:07:26,198
Hey!

865
01:07:26,292 --> 01:07:30,080
If you're afraid you'll wake
the kids, we don't have any.

866
01:08:31,691 --> 01:08:32,851
Abby!

867
01:08:38,990 --> 01:08:40,446
Abby!

868
01:08:46,789 --> 01:08:48,199
Abby!

869
01:08:48,333 --> 01:08:50,119
