they'd find us, and it gets Ray killed.

882
01:09:25,912 --> 01:09:28,244
- But if you testify...
- The FBI says they'll help Ray

883
01:09:28,331 --> 01:09:30,743
- and protect us.
- Protect what?

884
01:09:34,087 --> 01:09:36,419
What are you going to do?

885
01:09:37,757 --> 01:09:40,590
Go in tomorrow and start to copy files.

886
01:09:40,718 --> 01:09:42,208
I don't have a choice.

887
01:09:42,303 --> 01:09:44,544
Mitch,

888
01:09:44,639 --> 01:09:46,675
what are you saying?

889
01:09:46,766 --> 01:09:48,757
You'll be revealing clients' secrets.

890
01:09:48,893 --> 01:09:50,303
- You'll be disbarred.
- Abby, don't...

891
01:09:50,436 --> 01:09:53,098
You'll never be able to practice
law again for the rest of your life.

892
01:09:53,231 --> 01:09:56,394
Everything you've worked for!
They can't ask you to do that!

893
01:09:56,484 --> 01:09:58,440
They are not asking!

894
01:10:06,119 --> 01:10:10,283
We have to behave exactly as we have been.

895
01:10:11,416 --> 01:10:15,500
We have to go to work and come home every day

896
01:10:16,254 --> 01:10:20,088
and never wonder about the walls and the wires...

897
01:10:20,174 --> 01:10:22,460
And do nothing we want to do.

898
01:10:37,275 --> 01:10:39,641
Szechwan beef from Wong Boys.

899
01:10:40,528 --> 01:10:43,486
That was the last time I remember laughing.

900
01:10:44,949 --> 01:10:47,531
- Come on! Every single day we got...
- Oh, not you again, man.

901
01:10:47,660 --> 01:10:49,400
one of your trucks out here, blocking this alley.

902
01:10:49,495 --> 01:10:51,110
- Hey, leave me alone.
- What's it gonna take, huh?

903
01:10:51,205 --> 01:10:52,411
Hey, would you leave me alone, buddy?

904
01:10:52,498 --> 01:10:54,614
You're using this place as a parking lot!

905
