980
01:16:56,362 --> 01:16:57,477
- Why would Avery think...
- How do you know

981
01:16:57,571 --> 01:16:59,027
you weren't followed?

982
01:17:03,702 --> 01:17:07,490
Picture Abby one day walking to the mail box,

983
01:17:07,581 --> 01:17:12,200
anticipating the arrival of her
Redbook, her Sharper Image catalog.

984
01:17:13,504 --> 01:17:15,711
What does she find instead?

985
01:17:16,590 --> 01:17:18,751
