a trusting young wife to forgive

993
01:17:50,374 --> 01:17:52,456
and impossible to forget.

994
01:17:59,300 --> 01:18:03,009
That's just the kind of stuff the
FBI could use for coercion, Mitch.

995
01:18:03,095 --> 01:18:05,086
So you watch yourself.

996
01:18:05,931 --> 01:18:08,798
I'll do the best I can to protect you,

997
01:18:08,934 --> 01:18:12,426
and I know you will do your best to protect the Firm.

998
01:18:13,314 --> 01:18:16,977
