1734
02:26:38,540 --> 02:26:42,874
It's you at the dog track. I
could have gone public with it.

1735
02:26:42,961 --> 02:26:45,748
- Why didn't you?
- It's against the law.

1736
02:26:51,553 --> 02:26:52,963
Okay.

1737
02:26:55,890 --> 02:26:59,758
How in the hell did you ever come up with mail fraud?

1738
02:27:01,062 --> 02:27:03,053
It was on the bar exam.

1739
02:27:04,441 --> 02:27:07,057
They made me study like hell for it.

1740
02:27:43,563 --> 02:27:47,647
Well, you've had a busy day.

1741
02:27:50,487 --> 02:27:52,148
So did you.

1742
02:27:54,657 --> 02:27:57,615
Why didn't you tell me the truth about your plan?

1743
02:27:57,744 --> 02:27:59,780
All of it? The Moroltos.

1744
02:28:00,413 --> 02:28:04,122
Because I knew you'd worry,
and that might make you stay.

1745
02:28:05,460 --> 02:28:07,917
And I knew you needed to leave.

1746
02:28:18,014 --> 02:28:20,756
I like what you've done to the place.

1747
02:28:21,768 --> 02:28:24,976
- I thought you were going to your folks'.
- I was.

1748
02:28:27,357 --> 02:28:29,018
Some detour.

1749
02:28:32,612 --> 02:28:34,148
Where are you going?

1750
02:28:34,280 --> 02:28:35,986
To look for you.

1751
02:28:40,662 --> 02:28:44,951
I guess I didn't feel I could leave
you without trying to help you.

1752
02:28:48,503 --> 02:28:51,290
Do you want to tell me what happened?

1753
02:28:54,509 --> 02:28:56,170
Someday.

1754
02:28:58,179 --> 02:29:02,513
I think you should know that Avery was pretty decent.

1755
02:29:05,353 --> 02:29:09,437
He was decent, and corrupt,

1756
02:29:09,524 --> 02:29:11,890
and ruined, and so unhappy...

1757
02:29:12,026 --> 02:29:13,061
Listen, Abby...

1758
02:29:13,194 --> 02:29:15,105
And it could have happened to you, all of it.

1759
02:29:15,196 --> 02:29:16,686
You were on your way.

1760
02:29:16,823 --> 02:29:18,404
Did I lose you?

1761
02:29:25,373 --> 02:29:26,533
You look tired.

1762
02:29:26,666 --> 02:29:27,872
Did I?

1763
02:29:39,846 --> 02:29:42,053
I've loved you all my life.

1764
02:29:44,350 --> 02:29:46,136
Even before we met.

1765
02:29:48,897 --> 02:29:52,685
Part of it wasn't even you,
it was just a promise of you.

1766
02:29:54,027 --> 02:29:58,646
But these last days, you kept your promise.

1767
02:30:06,331 --> 02:30:08,242
How could you lose me?

1768
02:30:41,199 --> 02:30:44,191
- You think it will make it?
- Make it where?

1769
02:30:45,537 --> 02:30:47,198
Boston.

1770
02:30:47,288 --> 02:30:49,028
What's in Boston?

1771
02:30:49,707 --> 02:30:51,038
We are.

1772
02:30:53,920 --> 02:30:57,037
And the Wong Boys, and my kids.

1773
02:30:58,883 --> 02:31:02,467
And a very small unknown law firm.

1774
02:31:02,554 --> 02:31:04,590
With a lot of potential.

1775
02:31:05,807 --> 02:31:07,047
Yeah.

